                    <h3>Designing for AI</h3>
                    <p>Although leaps and bounds have been made in LLMs and consumer AI, iOT usecases beyond on/off, scheduling, volume up/down, tracking, and settings modes remain scarce. I's critical to be discerning of what user problems are actually getting solved.</p>
